    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Paweł Liskowski</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:155px;\"><a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=qmcgLRoAAAAJ&amp;hl=en\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/b/b7/PawelLiskowski.jpg\" width=\"153\" height=\"153\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:PawelLiskowski.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Paweł Liskowski <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Paweł Liskowski</b>,<br />\na Polish computer scientist and assistant professor at the Institute of Computing Science, \n<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pozna%C5%84_University_of_Technology\">Poznań University of Technology</a>. \nHis research interest include various subfields of <a href=\"/Artificial_Intelligence\" title=\"Artificial Intelligence\">artificial intelligence</a>, \nsuch as <a href=\"/Genetic_Programming#EvolutionaryComputation\" title=\"Genetic Programming\">evolutionary computation</a>, <a href=\"/Genetic_Programming\" title=\"Genetic Programming\">genetic programming</a>, \n<a href=\"/Deep_Learning\" title=\"Deep Learning\">deep learning</a>, <a href=\"/Reinforcement_Learning\" title=\"Reinforcement Learning\">reinforcement learning</a>, <a href=\"/Learning\" title=\"Learning\">machine learning</a> and <a href=\"/Pattern_Recognition\" title=\"Pattern Recognition\">pattern recognition</a> \n<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. His 2012 master's thesis focuses on comparison and analysis of methods that <a href=\"/Learning\" title=\"Learning\">learn</a> the <a href=\"/Othello\" title=\"Othello\">Othello</a> position evaluation <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2012_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2012 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pawe%C5%82_Liskowski&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2012_...\">2012 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pawe%C5%82_Liskowski&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2012 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Paweł Liskowski</a> (<b>2012</b>). <i>Co-Evolution versus Evolution with Random Sampling for Acquiring Othello Position Evaluation</i>. Master’s thesis, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pozna%C5%84_University_of_Technology\">Poznań University of Technology</a>, advisor <a href=\"/Wojciech_Ja%C5%9Bkowski\" title=\"Wojciech Jaśkowski\">Wojciech Jaśkowski</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.put.poznan.pl/wjaskowski/pub/var/pliskowski_msc.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Paweł Liskowski</a> (<b>2013</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dl.acm.org/doi/10.1145/2464576.2482752\">Quantitative Analysis of the Hall of Fame Coevolutionary Archives</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/gecco/gecco2013.html\">GECCO '13</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Marcin_Szubert\" title=\"Marcin Szubert\">Marcin Szubert</a>, <a href=\"/Wojciech_Ja%C5%9Bkowski\" title=\"Wojciech Jaśkowski\">Wojciech Jaśkowski</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Paweł Liskowski</a>, <a href=\"/Krzysztof_Krawiec\" title=\"Krzysztof Krawiec\">Krzysztof Krawiec</a> (<b>2013</b>). <i>Shaping Fitness Function for Evolutionary Learning of Game Strategies</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/gecco/gecco2013.html\">GECCO 2013</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.put.poznan.pl/wjaskowski/pub/papers/szubert2013shaping.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Wojciech_Ja%C5%9Bkowski\" title=\"Wojciech Jaśkowski\">Wojciech Jaśkowski</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Paweł Liskowski</a>, <a href=\"/Marcin_Szubert\" title=\"Marcin Szubert\">Marcin Szubert</a>, <a href=\"/Krzysztof_Krawiec\" title=\"Krzysztof Krawiec\">Krzysztof Krawiec</a> (<b>2013</b>). <i>Improving Coevolution by Random Sampling</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/gecco/gecco2013.html\">GECCO 2013</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.put.poznan.pl/mszubert/pub/jaskowski2013gecco.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Wojciech_Ja%C5%9Bkowski\" title=\"Wojciech Jaśkowski\">Wojciech Jaśkowski</a>, <a href=\"/Marcin_Szubert\" title=\"Marcin Szubert\">Marcin Szubert</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Paweł Liskowski</a> (<b>2014</b>). <i>Multi-Criteria Comparison of Coevolution and Temporal Difference Learning on Othello</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/evoW/evoappl2014.html\">EvoApplications 2014</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.springer.com/gp/book/9783662455227\">Applications of Evolutionary Computation</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pawe%C5%82_Liskowski&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Marcin_Szubert\" title=\"Marcin Szubert\">Marcin Szubert</a>, <a href=\"/Wojciech_Ja%C5%9Bkowski\" title=\"Wojciech Jaśkowski\">Wojciech Jaśkowski</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Paweł Liskowski</a>, <a href=\"/Krzysztof_Krawiec\" title=\"Krzysztof Krawiec\">Krzysztof Krawiec</a> (<b>2015</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-319-16549-3_32\">The Role of Behavioral Diversity and Difficulty of Opponents in Coevolving Game-Playing Agents</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/evoW/evoappl2015.html\">EvoApplications 2015</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Paweł Liskowski</a>, <a href=\"/Krzysztof_Krawiec\" title=\"Krzysztof Krawiec\">Krzysztof Krawiec</a> (<b>2016</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://europepmc.org/article/med/27046869\">Segmenting Retinal Blood Vessels With Deep Neural Networks</a></i>. <a href=\"/IEEE#TMI\" title=\"IEEE\">IEEE Transactions on Medical Imaging</a>, Vol. 35, No. 11</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Wojciech_Ja%C5%9Bkowski\" title=\"Wojciech Jaśkowski\">Wojciech Jaśkowski</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Paweł Liskowski</a>, <a href=\"/Marcin_Szubert\" title=\"Marcin Szubert\">Marcin Szubert</a>, <a href=\"/Krzysztof_Krawiec\" title=\"Krzysztof Krawiec\">Krzysztof Krawiec</a> (<b>2016</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://content.sciendo.com/view/journals/amcs/26/1/article-p215.xml\">The performance profile: A multi–criteria performance evaluation method for test–based problems</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Journal_of_Applied_Mathematics_and_Computer_Science\">International Journal of Applied Mathematics and Computer Science</a>, Vol. 26, No. 1</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Paweł Liskowski</a>, <a href=\"/Wojciech_Ja%C5%9Bkowski\" title=\"Wojciech Jaśkowski\">Wojciech Jaśkowski</a>, <a href=\"/Krzysztof_Krawiec\" title=\"Krzysztof Krawiec\">Krzysztof Krawiec</a> (<b>2017</b>). <i>Learning to Play Othello with Deep Neural Networks</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1711.06583\">arXiv:1711.06583</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Paweł Liskowski</a>, <a href=\"/Wojciech_Ja%C5%9Bkowski\" title=\"Wojciech Jaśkowski\">Wojciech Jaśkowski</a>, <a href=\"/Krzysztof_Krawiec\" title=\"Krzysztof Krawiec\">Krzysztof Krawiec</a> (<b>2018</b>). <i>Learning to Play Othello with Deep Neural Networks</i>. <a href=\"/IEEE#TOG\" title=\"IEEE\">IEEE Transactions on Games</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Paweł Liskowski</a> (<b>2018</b>). <i>Heuristic Algorithms for Discovery of Search Objectives in Test-based Problems</i>. Ph.D. thesis, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pozna%C5%84_University_of_Technology\">Poznań University of Technology</a>, advisor <a href=\"/Krzysztof_Krawiec\" title=\"Krzysztof Krawiec\">Krzysztof Krawiec</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.put.poznan.pl/pliskowski/pub/phdthesis.pdf\">pdf</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pawe%C5%82_Liskowski&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.put.poznan.pl/pliskowski/\">Paweł Liskowski | Institute of Computing Science</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=qmcgLRoAAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Paweł Liskowski - Google Scholar Citations</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pawe%C5%82_Liskowski&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=qmcgLRoAAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Paweł Liskowski - Google Scholar Citations</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.put.poznan.pl/pliskowski/\">Paweł Liskowski | Institute of Computing Science</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Paweł Liskowski</a> (<b>2012</b>). <i>Co-evolution versus Evolution with Random Sampling for Acquiring Othello Position Evaluation</i>. master's thesis, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pozna%C5%84_University_of_Technology\">Poznań University of Technology</a>, supervisor <a href=\"/Wojciech_Ja%C5%9Bkowski\" title=\"Wojciech Jaśkowski\">Wojciech Jaśkowski</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.put.poznan.pl/wjaskowski/pub/var/pliskowski_msc.pdf\">pdf</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/l/Liskowski:Pawel.html\">dblp: Pawel Liskowski</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.put.poznan.pl/pliskowski/publications/\">Paweł Liskowski | Publications</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edax_(computing)\">Edax</a> by <a href=\"/Richard_Delorme\" title=\"Richard Delorme\">Richard Delorme</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301042153\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.018 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.019 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 107/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 234/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152